🔑 SSH Brute Force Detection
🎯 MITRE
T1110
🔍 Logic

Multiple failed login attempts

💻 SPL
index=* "Failed password"
| stats count by src_ip
| where count > 5
📊 Example
Failed password for invalid user
⚠️ False Positives
user typing wrong password
⚙️ Tuning
increase threshold (10+ attempts)
🔥 Severity

MEDIUM → HIGH
